sp.p:
Louise —dear Louise! (She looks up with sudden joy —Latour touches him warningly;
       he makes an effort to be calm) Be assured that whatever I do, is for your happiness.
       Who has told you otherwise ?

Yourself? I wish you were proscribed! You'd know what that meant, if you lived in Paris;
       but as my ally, Bokes, says, nobody understands anything here. This is what proscribing
       means, in a civilized country (holds up her model guillotine).
